  "@id": "https://bio.tools/peptide_modeling_services",
  "@type": "sc:SoftwareApplication",
  "dcterms:conformsTo": "https://bioschemas.org/profiles/ComputationalTool/0.6-DRAFT",
  "sc:description": "Peptides are made up of amino acid molecules, which are the \"building blocks\" of proteins. Peptides are short proteins, approximately 2-100 amino acids in length. CD ComputaBio offers a range of peptide modeling services to assist researchers and pharmaceutical companies in peptide drug discovery and development.",
